# ☕ Cafetería SASS – Responsive Coffee Shop Website

Cafetería SASS is a study project built as a responsive website for a coffee shop. Developed using HTML5, SASS, CSS Grid, and Gulp, the project features a clean, modern layout and structured, scalable styling.

> ⚠️ Note: This is a front-end prototype designed for educational and portfolio purposes.

## 🔗 Live Preview

[👉 View the Demo on Netlify](https://cafeteria-juligeraldev.netlify.app/)

## ✨ Features

- Responsive Design  
- SASS Architecture  
- CSS Grid Layouts  
- Gulp Automation  
- Custom Fonts  

